  "texts": [
    "Like any study, this study has several limitations that suggest potential paths for future research: The executives self-reported every skill and competency retrieved from the professional social network.",
    "Hence, executives may have exaggerated their qualifications to appear more qualified online.",
    "This potential bias is not specific to professional social networks.",
    "Executives might also exaggerate their skills in offline CVs or the information firms publish about their executives on their websites.",
    "Future research should develop study designs that allow the usage of measurement tools that do not depend on self-reporting."
  ],
  "correct_citations": []
}